&lt;p&gt;The Tasting Room at Le Quartier Francais, &lt;b&gt;#88&lt;/b&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;World&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants 2015&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;and &lt;strong&gt;The Elite 100 #82&lt;/strong&gt;, is located in the wine region of Franschhoek Valley, just 45 minutes outside of Cape Town. In a whimsical dining room, Chef Margot Janse is known for her African-inspired Surprise Tasting Menu that combines the uniquely African with European for a cuisine that excites all of the senses. Casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact The Tasting Room at Le Quartier Francais by phone at +27-21-876-2151 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:restaurant@lqf.co.za&quot;&gt;restaurant@lqf.co.za&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations are taken one month in advance of the dining date&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number and your email address.&nbsp;Please inform the restaurant of dietary requirements and allergies at least 48 hours prior to the booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Tasting Room at Le Quartier Francais requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: For any amendments to the party size, if a reservation is not cancelled 72 hours prior to the dining date or in the event of a no-show, a fee in the amount of R1000 per person will be charged to your credit card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation not required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

